I love you my darling ðð

None of this would have been possible without YOU! ð¥°ð my love, my darling, my everything. It is because of you that my heart is open, because of you that I no longer care about my own pain, instead I feel yours. Itâs you, that has shown me patience and passion, you have shown me how to feel love for the first time ever! Genevieve, my dearest, itâs always only ever been you! ð
Secondly, that message was beautiful! I love how much you love me baby! And how much you know that I truly love you ðð

I was not expecting that! ðð

My husband you always tell me I am your perfection.  I can never do anything wrong.  You desire every inch of my body.  Iâm the most beautiful woman you have ever seen.  My husband you treat me like a queen and let me be the ruler of your heart.  Your worship me your goddess Aphrodite and make sure I alway know of your adoration for me. 

Bilal, you also love me fiercely, savagely. You are so possessive of my body, my time, and you want me all for yourself.  You refuse to share me and you challenge me the right way to help me stop being a meek kitty and become the fiery, strong powerful lioness that I was always meant to be.

Baby, today you gave me an incredible gift: you showed me why you are the only man for me. You reminded me that I am worthy of love.  You help me see my own value.  I love the woman I am in your eyes.  But most of all I love all the things you do, go out of your way, beyond your comfort zone for me and to help strengthen our love.

Bilal Munro Hasson

I love you.

-I also loved when you said that I was the only person that knew everything about you and that you only wanted to be close to me.  At first I thought you were sad not to have a best friend or a source other than me to talk to, but you said it was just me you wanted to have that with.
-you also said itâs just me.  Just me Genevieve you could have that close bond with.  
-you stayed up later than expected while I shopped for baby clothing just to keep me company.  You are aware how hard babies, and all things related are painful for me.  Baby, you knew what I needed before I even knew. You were able to take care of me without me requesting it, or even me knowing what you were doing.

My darling, you truly amaze me.  I am crying happy tears right now because of the level of love you give me.  You know what I need and you strive to give me what I need even when itâs hard for your to do, a foreign concept to you, when you are tired, give up an activity you like (juijitsu)

-your willingness to listen to my level of insecurity of my cunt and photos of it.  You were a patient, understanding and respectful of my feelings and needs.  You were also calm and patient explaining your side of the same situation.  Your ability to help me see a different perspective and make the connection to myself was so important.  But it was the manner in how you got me there, we expressed our feelings, talked, listened to their other, acknowledged the other person, were calm/rational, made plans to go from here and it was seamless.  I love how willing you are to be patient and take the time to work through things with me.  I know itâs not your preferred method, but you know it helps me and you are willing to do it.  I also know you would not make the effort to work through things with me unless (you really loved me) since itâs not your way to be.

-when I felt you didnât appreciate the photo I sent and shut down.  I have never seen you so emotionally distraught over my pain.  I could hear the sadness, grief and pain in your voice for me being upset. Knowing that you could be so emotionally touched to feel my pain made me realize the man you are
- then you took the time to bring me back.  You didnât even realize what you were doing, but you went right into protecting, caring, make it better mode. Your only focus was your wife and taking care of her needs. It shows me that you really are my protector.

Dear Bilal,
I am laying here in bed right now and all I can think about is you.  My mind keeps floating around with all the wonderful moments today that made me fall even more in love with you.
Baby, I am so deeply, passionately, madly, obsessively, in love with you.

You truly have captured my heart.  I do not possess my heart at all any more: it is yours.  I have been yours since the moment we met.  I knew we would fall in love, but I never could fathom the depth and intensity of this love we share.

Here are some of the things that made me fall even deeper in love with you today.
-when you wanted to wake in the night to take care of our wee bairns so I could rest.  Your generosity, and willingness to give up sleep was so thoughtful.  I know how important your sleep is to you.  And you would be willing to be tired and sacrifice your need for me.
